Introduction

Kim Jungeun, known under her stage name Kim Lip, is a South Korean singer-songwriter and dancer under MODHAUS. She is a member of the project girl group ARTMS, and the leader of its second sub-unit, ODD EYE CIRCLE. She is also former member of the girl group LOONA.

She debuted on May 15, 2017, as a member and subsequently released her solo single album "Kim Lip" on May 23, 2017.

Kim Lip debuted as a member of LOONA on August 20, 2018, with their first mini album "[+ +]".

On May 31, 2024, Kim Lip debuted as a member of ARTMS with their first album "Dall".
